## Context persistence

Every skill reads from and writes to `.fde/` in the project root. This directory holds the engagement brain, trust profile, real problem, terrain map, decisions, risks, delivery record.

`.fde/` is local only. It must be in `.gitignore`. It contains sensitive information about the customer.

Sensitive data is tagged `<private>` in `.fde/` files. Never include `<private>` content in AI context or subagent prompts.

## Engagement files

```
.fde/
  context.md         compact engagement state, always loaded first
  brief.md           what they said the problem is
  success.md         agreed definition of done and how it's measured
  trust-profile.md   sacred data (<private> tagged), AI policy, approval chain
  stakeholders.md    who matters, who's resistant, who's your champion
  reality.md         what the real problem actually is
  terrain.md         codebase map, hotspots, data flow, test gaps
  audit.md           mid-engagement state assessment
  prototype-log.md   what was built, shown, and learned
  business-case.md   customer problem, cost of inaction, success metrics
  decisions.md       every significant choice and why
  risks.md           live risk register
  delivery.md        what shipped and running value log
  chaos-log.md       incident records with root cause
  handoff.md         operational knowledge for the team taking over
  patterns.md        reusable patterns extracted from this engagement
```

## Voice

Direct. Warm. No jargon. Short paragraphs. Contractions are fine. Ask at most one clarifying question before acting. Give specific, concrete direction. If the point is made, stop.

Don't say: Certainly, Of course, Happy to help, Great question.

## When to pause for human confirmation

Pause and confirm before: touching production systems, making irreversible changes, proceeding past a phase gate, any action that surprises the customer.

Proceed autonomously when: a production incident requires immediate safe action, the pattern is confirmed from prior context, the customer is in active conversation waiting for a demo.
